1115
01:13:55,719 --> 01:13:58,385
We, mothers, we always know. Don't we?

1116
01:13:59,234 --> 01:14:01,014
And you were ok with it?

1117
01:14:01,014 --> 01:14:02,007
Oh god, no.

1118
01:14:03,100 --> 01:14:07,094
