1124
01:14:26,594 --> 01:14:27,891
So don't talk.

1125
01:14:28,867 --> 01:14:30,337
Just come and listen.

1126
01:14:31,486 --> 01:14:33,139
I think you'll be shocked

1127
01:14:33,550 --> 01:14:38,751
at how many people think they were the All-American-Family.

1128
01:14:38,874 --> 01:14:40,111
I'll think about it.

1129
01:14:45,320 --> 01:14:48,303
Eric was taunted in shcool all the time.

1131
01:14:49,813 --> 01:14:50,960
Mary, you came.

1132
01:14:50,960 --> 01:14:52,045
I can't stay long.

1133
01:14:52,045 --> 01:14:53,221
That's great. Come on in.

1134
01:14:53,356 --> 01:14:56,453
I was so furious, I went to the principal.

1135
01:14:56,453 --> 01:14:59,920
But he didn't do a thing to the boys who did it.

1136
01:15:00,471 --> 01:15:02,306
I was shocked by that.

1137
01:15:02,794 --> 01:15:05,409
I called them fruits, and ferries.

1138
01:15:06,037 --> 01:15:07,030
I didn't know.

1139
01:15:07,621 --> 01:15:10,389
It took me a long time to accept my Sam.

1140
01:15:11,674 --> 01:15:13,266
I think I alway knew.

1141
01:15:13,480 --> 01:15:14,027
I mean...

1142
01:15:14,027 --> 01:15:18,396
He asked for a pink Lacoste shirt for his birthday.

1143
01:15:18,633 --> 01:15:20,408
He was always different.

1144
01:15:20,863 --> 01:15:22,748
So he tells me he's gay...

1145
01:15:23,054 --> 01:15:24,271
What do I do?

1146
01:15:24,311 --> 01:15:25,609
I take him hunting.

1147
01:15:25,701 --> 01:15:28,881
There he is in his pink Lacoste shirt, he saw a deer

1148
01:15:28,881 --> 01:15:31,345
