1155
01:15:55,869 --> 01:15:57,136
Ah, hello reverend!

1156
01:15:57,136 --> 01:15:58,201
Please, come sit down.

1157
01:15:58,201 --> 01:15:59,083
Hi guys!

1158
01:15:59,214 --> 01:16:00,217
Hi reverend!

1159
01:16:00,220 --> 01:16:02,272
Glad to see you're all here tonight.

1160
01:16:02,272 --> 01:16:07,554
As you may know, reverend Whitsell is a pastor of the Metropolitan Community Church,

1161
01:16:07,554 --> 01:16:11,974
and he's proposing a gay freedom day to the Walnut Creek city council.

1162
01:16:12,664 --> 01:16:15,596
The city council vote happens in about a month.

1163
01:16:15,596 --> 01:16:18,759
and I would love all your support.

1164
01:16:35,396 --> 01:16:35,802
Mary!

1165
01:17:12,952 --> 01:17:13,357
Mary?

1166
01:17:15,398 --> 01:17:17,983
Mary, what are you doing out here?

1167
01:17:18,643 --> 01:17:20,222
You're soak. Come inside.

1168
01:17:20,222 --> 01:17:22,513
I didn't know where else to go.

1169
01:17:28,906 --> 01:17:30,437
I was sitting there,

1170
01:17:30,931 --> 01:17:32,949
listening to all their stories.

1171
01:17:33,941 --> 01:17:35,178
About how they...

1172
01:17:35,728 --> 01:17:37,330
always just knew...

1173
01:17:37,882 --> 01:17:40,365
their kid was different.

1174
01:17:42,014 --> 01:17:44,548
And then I had this dream tonight...

1175
01:17:45,444 --> 01:17:46,965
Bobby was a baby.

1176
01:17:53,944 --> 01:17:56,306
My son was always different.

1177
01:18:00,755 --> 01:18:03,360
His difference began at conception.

1178
01:18:06,058 --> 01:18:07,173
I knew that.

1179
01:18:08,423 --> 01:18:09,305
I felt it.

1180
01:18:11,599 --> 01:18:12,481
I know now...

1181
01:18:13,419 --> 01:18:15,538
why God didn't heal Bobby

1182
01:18:17,572 --> 01:18:19,102
He didn't heal him because...

1183
01:18:21,809 --> 01:18:23,989
there was nothing wrong with him.

1184
01:18:26,797 --> 01:18:27,729
I did this!

1185
01:18:29,939 --> 01:18:31,521
I killed my son!

1186
01:18:31,872 --> 01:18:33,249
You did not kill your son.

1187
01:18:33,249 --> 01:18:34,314
Bobby killed himself.

1188
01:18:34,979 --> 01:18:36,814
How could God forgive me?

1189
01:18:38,846 --> 01:18:40,742
How could Bobby forgive me?

1190
01:18:41,708 --> 01:18:43,289
God has already done the forgiving.

1191
01:18:43,709 --> 01:18:46,294
You have to forgive yourself.

1192
01:18:47,899 --> 01:18:49,136
I'm so sorry!

1193
01:18:52,333 --> 01:18:53,752
I'm so sorry!

1194
01:19:05,207 --> 01:19:06,271
Dear god.

1195
01:19:06,698 --> 01:19:08,754
Give us something we can live with

1196
01:19:08,754 --> 01:19:14,701
and pass on to others whose lives will never be the same because of a loved one's death. 

1197
01:19:14,701 --> 01:19:17,124
I did not decide on brown eyes for myself.

1198
01:19:18,162 --> 01:19:21,700
And I now realize that Bobby didn't decide to be gay.

1199
01:19:22,486 --> 01:19:24,113
If you say in your word

1200
