that it is evil and wicked to be born with no arms,

1201
01:19:27,516 --> 01:19:29,756
and a child is born with no arms,

1202
01:19:30,592 --> 01:19:32,771
What is that child to think?

1203
01:19:39,185 --> 01:19:45,158
Our first order business is a proposal for a gay freedeom day in Walnut Creek.

1204
01:19:45,158 --> 01:19:46,517
Attention, please.

1205
01:19:46,800 --> 01:19:48,868
We have a select group to debate the issue.

1206
01:19:48,868 --> 01:19:49,715
I don't see her.

1207
01:19:49,715 --> 01:19:52,554
...it's reverend Whitsell.

1208
01:19:52,834 --> 01:19:53,706
For one day,

1209
01:19:54,882 --> 01:19:58,945
for one day, people can celebrate their difference rather than feel shame. 

1210
01:19:58,945 --> 01:20:00,719
They should be ashame!

1211
01:20:02,773 --> 01:20:07,095
There are so many other people who need our time and our attention.

1212
01:20:07,095 --> 01:20:09,112
Why are we wasting it on this?

1213
01:20:09,181 --> 01:20:12,472
Alright, alright. Let's have some order here please.

1214
01:20:12,472 --> 01:20:15,949
They spit in the face of decency and morality.

1215
01:20:17,784 --> 01:20:22,396
We cannot allow the fabric of our society to be torn apart.

1216
01:20:24,021 --> 01:20:24,488
Right?

1217
01:20:30,002 --> 01:20:33,611
I heard he tries to run for the Human Relations commission,

1218
01:20:33,652 --> 01:20:36,896
they picked that limped Whitsell instead.

1219
01:20:37,021 --> 01:20:38,795
They sent him a letter.

1220
01:20:38,902 --> 01:20:40,758
I said, 'We sing hymns at our church'.

1221
01:20:40,758 --> 01:20:42,904
What do you do with the hymns at your church?

1222
01:20:42,904 --> 01:20:45,467
So unless anyone else has anything else to add,

1223
01:20:45,467 --> 01:20:48,139
we'll adjourn to make our decision.

1224
01:20:48,139 --> 01:20:48,545
Mary?

1225
01:20:50,277 --> 01:20:50,855
Hey Dad!

1226
01:20:52,312 --> 01:20:53,184
Dad, get in here!

1227
01:20:54,176 --> 01:20:56,346
Dad hurry up! Mum's on TV.

1228
01:20:56,418 --> 01:20:58,591
Homosexuality is a sin.

1230
01:21:00,155 --> 01:21:03,248
Homosexuals are dommed to spend eternity in hell.

1232
01:21:04,633 --> 01:21:05,991
If they wanted to change,

1233
01:21:06,449 --> 01:21:09,531
they could be healed of their evil ways.

1234
01:21:09,531 --> 01:21:11,599
If they would turn away from temptation,

1235
01:21:12,202 --> 01:21:14,270
they could be normal again.

1236
01:21:14,346 --> 01:21:17,525
If only they would try and try harder,

1237
01:21:17,525 --> 01:21:18,883
if it doesn't work.

1238
01:21:19,248 --> 01:21:24,219
These are all the things I said to my son Bobby when I found out he was gay.

1239
01:21:24,219 --> 01:21:25,993
When he told me he was homosexual,

1240
01:21:25,993 --> 01:21:27,888
my world fell apart.

1241
01:21:28,556 --> 01:21:30,077
I did everything I could

1242
01:21:30,530 --> 01:21:32,476
to cure him of his sickness.

1243
01:21:33,689 --> 01:21:35,707
8 months ago, my son...

1244
01:21:35,707 --> 01:21:37,948
jumped off a bridge and killed himself.

1245
01:21:39,631 --> 01:21:44,471
I deeply regret my lack of knowledge about gay and lesbian people.

1246
01:21:44,471 --> 01:21:49,073
I see that everything I was taught and told was bigotry and dehumanizing slender.

1247
01:21:50,488 --> 01:21:54,086
If I had investigated, beyond what I was told,

1248
01:21:54,169 --> 01:21:56,125
if I had just,

1249
01:21:56,234 --> 01:21:57,582
listened to my son,

1250
01:21:59,024 --> 01:22:01,326
when he poured his heart out to me...

1251
01:22:01,869 --> 01:22:04,231
I would not be standing here today with you

1252
01:22:04,565 --> 01:22:06,227
filled with regrets.

1253
01:22:06,545 --> 01:22:07,427
I believe

1254
01:22:07,706 --> 01:22:11,607
that God was pleased with Bobby's kind and loving spirit.

1255
01:22:11,607 --> 01:22:12,912
In god's eyes

1256
01:22:12,912 --> 01:22:15,679
kindness and love are what it's all about.

1257
01:22:16,035 --> 01:22:21,225
I didn't know that each time that I echoed eternal damnation for gay people...

1258
01:22:21,273 --> 01:22:27,810
each time I referred to Bobby as sick and perverted and a danger to our children...

1259
01:22:27,810 --> 01:22:29,107
his self-esteem,

1260
01:22:29,861 --> 01:22:33,165
his sense of worth, were being destroyed.

1261
01:22:33,481 --> 01:22:34,423
and finally,

1262
01:22:34,872 --> 01:22:38,725
his spirit broke beyond repair.

1263
01:22:39,745 --> 01:22:45,391
It was not god's will that Bobby climbed over the side of a freeway overpass

1264
01:22:46,446 --> 01:22:48,253
and jumped directly into the path

1265
01:22:48,253 --> 01:22:52,571
of an 18 wheel truck which killed him instantly.

1266
01:22:53,447 --> 01:22:54,530
Bobby's death

1267
01:22:54,530 --> 01:23:00,491
was the direct result of his parents' ignorance and fear of the word gay.

1268
01:23:02,759 --> 01:23:04,472
He wanted to be a writer.

1269
01:23:06,602 --> 01:23:11,741
His hopes and dreams should not have been taken from him but they were.

1270
01:23:12,554 --> 01:23:13,436
They are children

1271
01:23:14,296 --> 01:23:15,289
like Bobby,

1272
01:23:16,225 --> 01:23:18,425
sitting in your congreggations,

1273
01:23:19,497 --> 01:23:20,977
unknown to you,

1274
01:23:21,114 --> 01:23:22,767
