1277
01:23:30,915 --> 01:23:32,436
Their prayers to god,

1278
01:23:32,436 --> 01:23:33,561
for understanding,

1279
01:23:33,983 --> 01:23:34,865
and acceptance,

1280
01:23:35,458 --> 01:23:36,806
and for your love.

1281
01:23:38,958 --> 01:23:40,834
But your hatred, and fear,

1282
01:23:41,772 --> 01:23:45,918
and ignorance of the word «gay» will silence those prayers

1283
01:23:47,315 --> 01:23:48,136
So...

1284
01:23:50,910 --> 01:23:52,624
before you echo «Amen»

1285
01:23:53,008 --> 01:23:55,542
in your home and place of worship.

1286
01:23:56,052 --> 01:23:56,579
Think!

1287
01:23:57,393 --> 01:23:58,752
Think and remember.

1288
01:23:59,750 --> 01:24:01,575
