1301
01:25:01,020 --> 01:25:02,074
Just in time!

1302
01:25:03,469 --> 01:25:04,968
Jacky, is this everyone?

1303
01:25:04,968 --> 01:25:06,144
Oh! honey, no...

1304
01:25:06,625 --> 01:25:07,446
Come with me.

1305
01:25:07,927 --> 01:25:09,596
We have a special place for you.

1306
01:25:09,596 --> 01:25:10,296
Ok .

1308
01:25:55,844 --> 01:25:58,490
To all the Bobby and Janes out there...

1309
01:25:58,571 --> 01:26:02,982
I say these words to you as I would with my own precious children.

1310
01:26:02,982 --> 01:26:05,078
Please don't give up hope on life.

1311
01:26:05,078 --> 01:26:06,071
Or yourselves.

1312
01:26:06,983 --> 01:26:08,933
You're very special to me.

1313
01:26:08,933 --> 01:26:14,343
