1314
01:26:14,343 --> 01:26:17,070
Promise me you'll keep trying.

1315
01:26:17,168 --> 01:26:18,992
Bobby gave up on love.

1316
01:26:19,049 --> 01:26:20,878
I hope you won't.

1317
01:26:20,878 --> 01:26:23,007
You're always in my gods.

1318
01:26:25,432 --> 01:26:27,490
My name is Bobby Griffith.

1319
01:26:27,897 --> 01:26:30,105
I write this in hope that one day,

1320
01:26:30,105 --> 01:26:31,575
many years from now,

1321
01:26:31,941 --> 01:26:33,462
I would be able to go back

1322
01:26:33,462 --> 01:26:35,339
and remember what my life was like,

1323
01:26:35,339 --> 01:26:38,041
when I was a young and confused adolescent,

1324
01:26:38,041 --> 01:26:42,178
desperately trying to understand myself in the world I live in

1325
01:26:42,178 --> 01:26:44,237
The other reason I write this,

1326
01:26:44,237 --> 01:26:46,460
so long after I died,

1327
01:26:46,460 --> 01:26:49,415
others may have a chance to read about me,

1328
01:26:49,415 --> 01:26:52,588
and see what my life as a young person was like.

